name: Green Lake Trail
description: The inner loop around Green Lake Park

name: Myrtle Edwards Park Trail
description: From the Seattle-Bainbridge Ferry Terminal, through the Sculpture Park, Myrtle Edwards Park, Centennial Park, to Elliott Bay Park, and back.

name: Alki Beach Trail
description: From the West Seattle Ferry Terminal at Seacrest Park to the Alki Point Lighthouse and back.

name: Fremont Trail
description: From Hale's Brewery through the Fremont neighborhood to Gasworks Park and back along the Burke-Gilman trail.

name: Arboretum Trail
description: A loop from the Arboretum's Botanical Gardens, through Foster Island, Marsh Island, over the 520 bridge, through the Japanese Garden, and back to the start.

name: Discovery Park Trail
description: The loop trail through Discovery Park

name: Volunteer Park Trail
description: A loop from Volunteer Park through the Montlake neighborhood, around the reservoir, and back to the start.

name: Golden Gardens Trail
description: From Meadow Point at the top of Golden Gardens Park, down to the Ballard Locks and back.

name: Magnuson Park Trail
description: A loop along the waterfront and frog trail in Magnuson Park.

name: Seward Park Trail
description: A loop around Bailey Peninsula in Seward Park.
